00:13:50,037 --> 00:13:54,792
{\an8}AS THEY SAY WE SHOULD BE
THE SALT OF THE EARTH,

125
00:13:54,792 --> 00:13:59,421
{\an8}THE IMAGE OF SALT FELT SIMILAR
TO THE GOOD FEELINGS OF WHITE

126
