{\an8}I THOUGHT OF A CUTE AND INNOCENT BABY

128
00:14:08,347 --> 00:14:12,101
{\an8}I THINK MILK SHOWS THE INNOCENCE OF WHITE

129
00:14:15,354 --> 00:14:19,233
{\an8}EVERY WHITE THING FELT THE SAME TO ME

130
00:14:19,233 --> 00:14:21,443
{\an8}AND I COULDN'T FIGURE OUT YOUR INTENTIONS

131
00:14:21,443 --> 00:14:23,529
{\an8}WHEN YOU TOLD ME TO FIND THE TRUE WHITE

132
