BECAUSE I CAN'T HEAR PEOPLE
ANSWERING THE DOOR,

292
00:27:43,953 --> 00:27:48,083
I CAN ONLY EITHER OPEN THE DOOR
WITHOUT PERMISSION AND BE A RUDE PERSON

293
