MOEUN, YOU REACHED OUT TO ME

296
00:28:03,348 --> 00:28:10,105
WHEN I WASN'T AWARE THAT THERE WAS A FIRE

297
00:28:16,861 --> 00:28:21,574
SO IF SOMETHING HAPPENS
