539
00:47:49,491 --> 00:47:50,534
Excuse me?

540
00:47:53,954 --> 00:47:57,583
You're Jung Modam. How could you be Jaden?

541
00:47:57,583 --> 00:48:00,335
I will do my best
to turn your worries to relief,

542
00:48:00,335 --> 00:48:03,255
